New endorsement deal with a popular smartphone brand has left Nigerian songstress Tiwa Savage excited. The 42-year-old singer and mother of one took to her Instagram account to announce her newest endorsement deal in a video.   Entertainers thrill on International Music Day in Lagos     Having great voice is a tip of iceberg, Raquel Hage     Sanwo-Olu eager to partner filmmakers to showcase Lagos,…   Explaining the video, she wrote, “This one is highly approved by the No 1 ABG, Your girl is on board with one of the coolest brands ever – Tecno. Show some love to my newest family. I am so excited.” Savage is currently on a tour of cities in the United States of America to promote her ‘Water and Garri’ EP. Meanwhile, the smartphone brand has expressed confidence in its choice of Savage as its brand ambassador and the perfect candidate to promote the brand and its products.